snippet.title: S.S Lucifer - Man Overboard! (Mega Drive)
snippet.description:
Now personally I never owned this game when it came out, but when I was renting some Mr Bean VHS tapes from Ritz Videos near 1995, I also found this game available to rent until it went off the market near 1998 for the newer 32/64-bit early console games.

1994 (c) Codemasters
